track_notes:
One of the most beautiful sharp summits in NW Italy.
Road closed in winter , NO camper or caravan allowed on the road to Colle Valcavera.  
Easy but long trail to the base of the mountain and then steep rise on the rocks.
There is always a lot of people rising to the top , so helmet is essential to prevent rolling stones.
track_title: Class EE - SHARP ROCK - Helmet -  NO phone

track_notes:
Parcheggio al colle del Preit. PARKING FEE 10 Euros a day in summer. Easy track to the base of the rock. 
Then STEEP RISE ON THEW ROCKS. Too many people on top in sunday or saturday, its better go there on tuesday like me. 
Meglio evitare i giorni festivi con cima affollata.
Il CASCO serve a proteggersi dalle pietre smosse dai molti sciamannati che non sanno scendere.
track_title: classif EE HELMET advised -  summit rocky  and crowded
